==Martuthunira==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/majili/}}
===Etymology===
From Proto-Ngayarda ''*mayirli'', from Proto-Pama-Nyungan ''*mayi''.
===Nominals===
'''mayili'''

# [[paternal grandfather]], father's father
